<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            color: #000;
        }

        .item {
            color: #000;
        }

        .item+.item {
            margin-top: 16px;
        }

        .title {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 20px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .message {
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: 600;
            background-color: #6E3FF3;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .important {
            padding-left: 20px;
            margin: 0px;
        }

        .important p {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 0 0 8px -20px;
        }

        .important li {
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .closing {
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="title item">
        {{clientName}} - {{jobTitle}} - {{candidateName}}
    </div>
    <div class="greeting item">
        Dear admin,
    </div>
    <div class="message item">
        A new candidate has been submitted by a recruiter. Below are the details of the submission:
    </div>
    <ul class="important item">
        <li>Candidate ID: {{candidateId}}</li>
        <li>Candidate Name: {{candidateName}}</li>
        <li>Position Applied For: {{jobTitle}}</li>
        <li>Client: {{clientName}}</li>
        <li>Date of Submission: {{submissionDate}}</li>
        <li>Recruiter Name: {{recruiterName}}</li>
        <li>Contact Channel: {{contactChannel}}</li>
        <li>Group chat: {{groupChat}}</li>
    </ul>
    <a href={{link}} class="button item">Check new candidate</a>
    <div class="message item">
        Please review the submission at your earliest convenience. If further details are required, feel free to reach
        out.
    </div>
    <div class="message item">
        Thank you for your prompt attention.
    </div>
    <div class="closing item">
        Best regards,
        <br />
        KitesHR Support Team
    </div>
</body>

</html>